{"article_id":"IMDgiALOy41TyUgO","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"Democrats have vowed to pass bills","depth":7},{"id":1,"text":"that would end a government shutdown","depth":7},{"id":2,"text":"as they took control of the US House of Representatives on Thursday .","depth":6},{"id":3,"text":"But the bills will not include funding for President Donald Trump 's Mexican border wall , the cause of the shutdown .","depth":5},{"id":4,"text":"The impasse will therefore continue ,","depth":5},{"id":5,"text":"as Republicans still control the Senate","depth":6},{"id":6,"text":"and say","depth":7},{"id":7,"text":"they will not pass the funding bills","depth":8},{"id":8,"text":"without Mr Trump 's approval .","depth":8},{"id":9,"text":"The partial shutdown has now lasted 13 days ,","depth":5},{"id":10,"text":"affecting some 800,000 workers .","depth":5},{"id":11,"text":"Shutdowns occur","depth":5},{"id":12,"text":"when Congress fails to approve a budget for government operations ,","depth":6},{"id":13,"text":"or the president refuses to sign it , by a certain deadline .","depth":6},{"id":14,"text":"Mr Trump 's Republicans had passed a budget bill","depth":7},{"id":15,"text":"including $ 5bn","depth":9},{"id":16,"text":"( £4bn )","depth":9},{"id":17,"text":"funding for the wall","depth":8},{"id":18,"text":"in December ,","depth":8},{"id":19,"text":"when they still had a majority in the House","depth":8},{"id":20,"text":"but they could not get the necessary 60 votes in the 100-seat Senate .","depth":7},{"id":21,"text":"The House majority has passed to the Democrats","depth":6},{"id":22,"text":"following the November mid-term elections .","depth":6},{"id":23,"text":"Nancy Pelosi ,","depth":9},{"id":24,"text":"who is the new House majority leader ,","depth":9},{"id":25,"text":"said","depth":8},{"id":26,"text":"the Democrats would quickly pass budget legislation","depth":8},{"id":27,"text":"providing sufficient funds","depth":9},{"id":28,"text":"to end the shutdown .","depth":9},{"id":29,"text":"But she was quite clear","depth":8},{"id":30,"text":"what it would not include .","depth":8},{"id":31,"text":"Speaking on the Today show on Thursday ,","depth":10},{"id":32,"text":"she reiterated :","depth":10},{"id":33,"text":"`` Nothing for the wall . ''","depth":9},{"id":34,"text":"`` There is no amount of persuasion","depth":12},{"id":35,"text":"he can do","depth":12},{"id":36,"text":"to say to us ,","depth":12},{"id":37,"text":"'We want you to do something","depth":13},{"id":38,"text":"that is not effective ,","depth":14},{"id":39,"text":"that costs billions of dollars , ' ''","depth":14},{"id":40,"text":"she said .","depth":10},{"id":41,"text":"`` That sends the wrong message about who we are as a country . ''","depth":9},{"id":42,"text":"Ms Pelosi also said","depth":7},{"id":43,"text":"she believed","depth":8},{"id":44,"text":"a sitting president could be indicted","depth":8},{"id":45,"text":"- although Justice Department guidelines disagree .","depth":6},{"id":46,"text":"The Democrats will try again to pass the blame for the shutdown on to the president ,","depth":8},{"id":47,"text":"pointing out","depth":9},{"id":48,"text":"that the bills","depth":12},{"id":49,"text":"they will pass","depth":12},{"id":50,"text":"would be similar to legislation","depth":11},{"id":51,"text":"that had won bipartisan support in the Senate in December","depth":11},{"id":52,"text":"before Mr Trump signalled","depth":12},{"id":53,"text":"he would not back it .","depth":12},{"id":54,"text":"`` We 're asking the president to open up government , ''","depth":9},{"id":55,"text":"Ms Pelosi said .","depth":9},{"id":56,"text":"`` We have given the Republicans a chance","depth":9},{"id":57,"text":"to take yes for an answer . ''","depth":9},{"id":58,"text":"One Democrat bill would temporarily fund the Department of Homeland Security until 8 February ,","depth":7},{"id":59,"text":"while another measure would fund other departments","depth":8},{"id":60,"text":"closed by the partial shutdown until 30 September .","depth":8},{"id":61,"text":"The Senate majority leader , Mitch McConnell , has said","depth":8},{"id":62,"text":"Republicans there will not back measures","depth":9},{"id":63,"text":"that Mr Trump does not support .","depth":9},{"id":64,"text":"He called the Democrats ' move a `` total nonstarter '' and a `` political sideshow '' .","depth":7},{"id":65,"text":"The BBC 's David Willis says","depth":7},{"id":66,"text":"the legislation would be dead on arrival in the Senate .","depth":7},{"id":67,"text":"He held a meeting with congressional leaders in the situation room of the White House on Thursday .","depth":8},{"id":68,"text":"Mr Trump sought to frame the discussion more in the context of national security than budgetary matters .","depth":8},{"id":69,"text":"There was no agreement with the Democrats ,","depth":8},{"id":70,"text":"although talks will continue on Friday .","depth":8},{"id":71,"text":"US media reported","depth":8},{"id":72,"text":"that Mr Trump ,","depth":9},{"id":73,"text":"when asked","depth":12},{"id":74,"text":"why he would not end the shutdown ,","depth":12},{"id":75,"text":"had said :","depth":11},{"id":76,"text":"`` I would look foolish","depth":11},{"id":77,"text":"if I did that . ''","depth":11},{"id":78,"text":"A White House official later told Associated Press","depth":8},{"id":79,"text":"this meant Mr Trump believed","depth":9},{"id":80,"text":"it would be foolish not to pay for border security .","depth":9},{"id":81,"text":"In his first cabinet meeting of the new year , the president said","depth":8},{"id":82,"text":"the shutdown would last","depth":9},{"id":83,"text":"as long","depth":10},{"id":84,"text":"as it took","depth":11},{"id":85,"text":"to get his funding ,","depth":11},{"id":86,"text":"adding","depth":8},{"id":87,"text":"`` could be a long time","depth":9},{"id":88,"text":"or could be quickly '' .","depth":9},{"id":89,"text":"Mr Trump reportedly told Ms Pelosi","depth":8},{"id":90,"text":"she should support the wall","depth":8},{"id":91,"text":"as she was a `` good Catholic ''","depth":8},{"id":92,"text":"and the Vatican City had a wall .","depth":8},{"id":93,"text":"About 25 % of the US federal government has no funding","depth":4},{"id":94,"text":"Nine departments have been affected ,","depth":6},{"id":95,"text":"including Homeland Security , Justice , Housing , Agriculture , Commerce , Interior , and the Treasury","depth":6},{"id":96,"text":"Around 800,000 federal workers are now furloughed","depth":7},{"id":97,"text":"- that is ,","depth":8},{"id":98,"text":"temporarily laid off due to a lack of funding -","depth":8},{"id":99,"text":"or working without pay","depth":6},{"id":100,"text":"Science labs face repercussions","depth":5},{"id":101,"text":"as many federally employed scientists have stopped working","depth":5},{"id":102,"text":"Native American tribes","depth":6},{"id":103,"text":"who receive substantial federal funding","depth":6},{"id":104,"text":"are struggling","depth":5},{"id":105,"text":"More women than ever before won seats in Congress in the 2018 mid-terms .","depth":2}],"relations":[{"parent":211,"left":198,"right":210,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":198,"left":119,"right":197,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":119,"left":114,"right":118,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":114,"left":109,"right":113,"relation":"causal","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":109,"left":108,"right":3,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":108,"left":107,"right":2,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":107,"left":0,"right":1,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":113,"left":4,"right":112,"relation":"explanation","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":112,"left":5,"right":111,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":111,"left":6,"right":110,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":110,"left":7,"right":8,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":118,"left":115,"rig